<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='183:191'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='191:212'>　尚書詳解卷九　　　　　宋　胡士行　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='212:230'>洛誥第十五　　　　　　　　　周書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='230:253'>　大甲復亳成王卜洛而伊尹周公告歸所以處大臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='253:276'>　之變嚴萬世之防也然周尚有頑民未定故公未得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='276:281'>　遽去</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='281:305'>召公既相宅周公徃營成周<span class='krp-note'>使/</span>使來告卜作洛誥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='305:317'>　此序與召誥相顧成文</span><br/>
